; Coverage test for filters.cc
; Tests rewrite_posts::operator() account rewrite path where prev_account
; has xdata (prev_account->has_xdata branch)
; The account-rewrite directive triggers rewrite_posts in the filter chain.

account-rewrite Expenses:Food  Groceries:Food

2024/01/15 Store
    Expenses:Food             $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/20 Store
    Expenses:Food             $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-80.00  Assets:Cash
              $80.00  Groceries:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
